snippet.title: The Displacement - XXv Productions - Official Full Gameplay Video
snippet.description: A full official gameplay video of The Displacement by XXv Productions. The game was created by Jonathan Boakes, in 1998-99, who also conducts this playthrough. http://www.shadowtor.com/store to purchase the game, along with the latest Dark Fall, called Ghost Vigil.
